{"tid":2203413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周五起延長堂食至午夜 重開酒吧、卡啦ok、主題公園 惟四人限聚令持續 陳肇始：短期難放寬至 6 月水平","createTime":"2020-09-15T10:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T10:05:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"caded553f513712323aef0418feb99e1ae056d1b","tid":2203413,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情持續放緩，今日新增 4 宗確診個案全部都是輸入個案，無本地個案。政府下午開記者會，宣布周五（18 日）起進一步放寬社交距離措施，包括延長餐廳堂食時間至午夜，以及重開酒吧、卡啦ok、主題公園、派對房間等。不過多次用作票控示威者的四人限聚令，將繼續生效，公眾地方戴口罩亦繼續。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E8%B5%B7%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F%E8%87%B3%E5%8D%88%E5%A4%9C-%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7-%E5%8D%A1%E5%95%A6ok-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92-%E6%83%9F%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B-%E7%9F%AD%E6%9C%9F%E9%9B%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E8%87%B3-6-%E6%9C%88%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%2590%25A7-%25E5%258D%25A1%25E5%2595%25A6ok-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592-%25E6%2583%259F%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E8%2587%25B3-6-%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=d7ee8608\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%258D%2588%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%25